{"tid":842411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年被洗腦3小時 誤信旅游可賺錢","createTime":"2018-09-30T09:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T11:57:45.000Z","uid":195323,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe64ccb64044c8a3766dcc90c5b21592de52a101","tid":842411,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"9月26日<br />\n一名失業青年相信女網友的說話，以為旅游可以賺錢，之後青年跟女網友介紹下去了尖沙咀商業大廈聽講座！<br />\n<br />\n青年提及女網友是其中一個會員<br />\n7點開始講座，每1小時換一個人分享<br />\n又播片又問問題一齊又拍手<br />\n10點半後，青年跟其他人分别被一對一游說加入，幸好青年醒目没有被騙錢入會！<br />\n現場有太約二十個人。<br />\n<br />\n事後！青年覺得旅游X銷入會費太貴，又要叫朋友入會才免月費，上網查一查發現蘋果日報17年踢爆這公司！"},{"pid":"92b35b9f39700954bea80db92666df886765eccd","tid":842411,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcc4d5b40f03b848f08bd01374c5a3e02f3bf63","tid":842411,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d980d7369936c2a68cd4e66d17dcfcb899e722","tid":842411,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54013f624cf2a259cd6412b8fdbdbb15d73f302","tid":842411,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"唔去傳銷唔知身體好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/792719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/792719</a><br />\n<br />\n月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428a3bde3b3cc68153f781bb367c6dd738f5ef23","tid":842411,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"傳銷害人，不過都係害啲智商低於70嘅人啫，與正常人無關"},{"pid":"b71a6